    <%= render(AboutPageFieldComponent.new(title: "What made you develop carnage?", contents: "Back when I started lifting (early 2021), I tried to look for a decent workot tracker. There are a few with decent features out there, they all suffer from the same problems: They either rely on old scientific literature or are all paid, which might not be very appealing to a lot of people. Carnage is my attempt at fixing that.")) %>

