    <%= render(AboutPageFieldComponent.new(title: "What features does carnage have?", contents: "Pretty much everything other workout trackers have, with the exception of not having to pay for anything! However, contrary to most workout trackers, carnage is updated with the latest science (quality ALWAYS over quantity) and will take you to places no other workout tracker will ever do!")) %>
